text: The 1859 Shamakhi earthquake struck Shamakhi in the Baku Governorate (present- day Republic of Azerbaijan) of the Russian Empire, on 11 June. The earthquake had an estimated moment magnitude scale of 5.9 and caused moderate damage and killed approximately 100 people. ==Related pages== * List of earthquakes in Azerbaijan == References == Category:Earthquakes in Azerbaijan Category:Articles on pre-1900 earthquakes Category:June events Category:1859
title: 1859 Shamakhi earthquake
